      </arrangement>
      <processinfo id="aspace_daf65425657d2f1aaa92dd8e1f093a31">
         <head>Processing Information</head>
         <p>Collections are processed to a variety of levels, depending on the work necessary to make them usable, their perceived research value, the availability of staff, and competing priorities. The library attempts to provide a basic level of preservation and access for all collections as they are acquired, and does more extensive processing of higher priority collections as time and resources permit.</p>
         <p>The collection is comprised of material formerly classed as: Uncat MSS 356, Uncat MSS 357, Uncat MSS 358, Uncat MSS 359, Uncat MSS 360, Uncat MSS 361, Uncat MSS 362, Uncat MSS 363, Uncat MSS 364, Uncat MSS 365, Uncat MSS 366, Uncat MS Vault 481.</p>
         <p>The collection received preliminary processing at the time of acquisition. Further rehousing and description were carried out in 2014.</p>  
      </processinfo>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_f3b095378764dc55434b902c43e2670a">
